# What does Isidor think?

Isidor is super happy with the computer, but he would probably feel the same way with Windows too.
He doesn't know what Linux is but he's able to navigate around and do what he wants.

I'm sure though that not being able to run Fortnite will become a big deal one day.
I hope I can distract him with other games, or maybe to make him understand that he can't have everything under the sun.

